text: The New Caledonia Super Ligue 2015 season was the 42nd season of the FCF since its establishment in 1962. The champions were chosen to represent the New Caledonia Super Ligue in the 2017 OFC Champions League. ==Standings== ==References== ==External links== *Season at soccerway.com Category:New Caledonia Super Ligue seasons New Category:2015 in New Caledonian sport
